      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE COMES BILLY (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.77 beating Runway Blue. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Can continue on his winning ways. DR. ZAIDEN (1) flew the lids with a sensational early split and hit the frame with a 4.5 lengths second (24.49) over 435m at Sale. Expected to be in this for a long way. CARTMAN (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Sandown over 515m behind Commissioner (30.30) in a R/A FIN. Scored at his previous run. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. One of the main contenders. PAW ESTRELLA (8) was out of placings last time (24.51) at Sale in a Free For All, finishing fourth and beaten 5 lengths. Has four wins already from this draw.",
